(WarBarge is back, so hopefully, he will take his characters)

Vehement:


Staring at Bloodstryke for a mere moment, Vehement smirked.  How weak these 
heathens are, he thought.  Raising an arm, its shaped changed into a large 
cannon, a single missile rocketing out at Bloodstryke's abdomen.
